_sText:
Hey!
I finally release the first version of my jailmap called Caton.
It is a quite small one which has some cool **features:**

- LED Board for announcements
- colored way for announcements
- open pool
- cells got 2 floors
- lots of hidden buttons/weapons etc.!


**Zones:**

- Pool
- Kitchen
- Football
- Disco
- Theatre
- Locker Room

If you find any bugs, or got any suggestions: post it in the comments-section! I'm planning to release a v2 with better textures and lightning! I'm sorry, that I have no credits for the people which textures and prefabs i used. But, i thank everyone on Gamebanana and specially those who upload prefabs and textures! YOU GUYS ARE MY HEROES! ;)

dF.out!
